                            <comment id="13092556" author="jfarrell" created="Sun, 28 Aug 2011 21:47:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;configure.ac AC_CHECK_LIBS are necessary only for the clients use. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;LIBS = -lssl -lcrypto -lpthread&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following patch removes the dependencies added from configure.ac in the thrift compiler makefile compiler/cpp/Makefile&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
