    Thrift-1299: If SSL is available, &apos;thrift&apos; binary links against it&lt;br/&gt;
Patch: jfarrell&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Removes the dependencies added from configure.ac in the thrift compiler makefile.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
